                                                        % deaths prevented globally
                              
                 Business question
What % of total deaths could be prevented globally? 

              Query
SELECT
  SUM(possible_cancer_deaths)AS total_cases,
  SUM(deaths_prevented) AS total_prevented,
  ROUND(
	(SUM(deaths_prevented) / SUM(possible_cancer_deaths)) * 100,2 
	)AS percentage_prevented
FROM cancer_data;

                 Insight
This percentage shows how many lives  we are saving globally.

            Recommendation
Tracking our metrics should be done every year, our metrics should improve if our intervention is working 
